(gpt-5.1), Google (gemini-3-pro-preview), Together/Meta
(Llama-4-Maverick-17B-128E-Instruct), Anthropic (claude-opus-4-1), and
xAI (grok-4-1-fast-non-reasoning). Performance is summarized as both an
