overall rank ordering generally persists at the field level.}
\label{fig:grouped-bars}
\end{figure}

\begin{figure}[htbp]
\centering
\includegraphics[width=0.95\linewidth]{figures/fig4_5_strength_weakness.png}
\caption{Strongest and weakest academic field per model. Each horizontal
segment connects a model's lowest-scoring field (red) to its
highest-scoring field (green), exposing the magnitude of domain-level
variability that single overall scores would otherwise conceal.}
\label{fig:strength-weakness}
\end{figure}


